						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">only the last couple of writes have to fall within HBlank. That's just 8 cycles in a a window of ~28 cycles, so it isn't so hard to get right.</div><br />Better yet, it's actually 5 cycles: the write from <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">stx $2005</tt>, three cycles to fetch <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">sta $2006</tt>, and the write from <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">sta $2006</tt>.</div>

